OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1772025561
OL,3,CMurder investigation begins after man
OL,4,Cstabbed to death
OL,6,FA murder investigation has begun after
OL,7,Fa man in his 20s was stabbed in Winson
OL,8,FGreen.
OL,10,FWest Midlands Police were called to
OL,11,FWood Green Road shortly before 9 pm on
OL,12,FMonday, 23 February.
OL,14,FTwo men, aged 39 and 45, have been
OL,15,Farrested on suspicion of murder and
OL,16,Fremain in custody.
OL,18,FThe police have said Wood Green Road
OL,19,Fhas been cordoned off, as well as
OL,20,Froads nearby, which may lead to some
OL,21,Ftraffic disruption.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
