OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1772025561
OL,3,CMurder investigation begins after man
OL,4,Cstabbed to death
OL,6,FIn a statement, police said: "Two men
OL,7,Fhave been arrested on suspicion of
OL,8,Fmurder after the death of a man in
OL,9,FWinson Green.
OL,11,F"We were called to Wood Green Road,
OL,12,Fshortly before 9 pm last night,
OL,13,Falongside our colleagues from the
OL,14,Fambulance service, after a man was
OL,15,Fstabbed in the street. Despite the
OL,16,Fbest efforts of paramedics, the man,
OL,17,Fin his 20s, sadly died at the scene.
OL,19,F"Our thoughts are with his loved ones
OL,20,Fat this devastating time.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1772025561
OL,3,CMurder investigation begins after man
OL,4,Cstabbed to death
OL,6,F"A murder investigation has been
OL,7,Flaunched, and we're working to
OL,8,Festablish the full circumstances.
OL,10,F"We've arrested two men, aged 39 and
OL,11,F45, on suspicion of murder. They
OL,12,Fremain in custody as we continue with
OL,13,Four enquiries.
OL,15,F"Wood Green Road has been cordoned off
OL,16,Fas well as roads nearby, which may
OL,17,Flead to some traffic disruption.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1772025561
OL,3,CMurder investigation begins after man
OL,4,Cstabbed to death
OL,6,F"Our forensic team is at the scene,
OL,7,Fand detectives are reviewing CCTV and
OL,8,Fcarrying out other enquiries in the
OL,9,Farea.
OL,11,F"We would urge witnesses or people
OL,12,Fwith information, including mobile
OL,13,Fphone or dashcam footage, to please
OL,14,Fcontact us on 101 quoting log number
OL,15,F5652 of 23 February. Alternatively,
OL,16,Fcall Crimestoppers anonymously on 0800
OL,17,F555 111.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
